title: Eliminates a number of filing fees imposed on businesses by the department of state; repealers
summary: Eliminates a number of filing fees imposed on businesses by the department of state pursuant to the business corporation law, the executive law and the not-for-profit corporation law; eliminates fees related to start up, merger, consolidation or dissolution of a corporation.
actClause: AN ACT to repeal certain provisions of the business corporation law, the executive law and the not-for-profit corporation law, in relation to certain fees collected by the department of state
